content.title: Data & Services Panel
content.body:
Select the Data & Services tab on the top-right of your canvas. It opens the Data & Services panel.

The Data & Services panel has Sample Services and Project Services.

  • Sample Services: These are the pre-bundled services with the sample data to help you get started.
  • Project Services: These are the services which are used by this project.
    You can create and configure new Volt MX Foundry services under Project Services.
